<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <% const pageSeo = (typeof seo !== 'undefined' && seo) ? seo : {}; %>
  <% const pageVisitorCount = (typeof visitorCount !== 'undefined' && visitorCount !== null) ? visitorCount : 0; %>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= pageSeo.title || 'WorkBuddy 新手教程' %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="<%= pageSeo.description || 'WorkBuddy 新手落地页：3步快速上手与实战场景提示词。' %>" />
  <meta name="keywords" content="<%= pageSeo.keywords || 'WorkBuddy,AI办公,提示词' %>" />
  <meta name="robots" content="index,follow,max-image-preview:large" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:locale" content="zh_CN" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="<%= pageSeo.title || 'WorkBuddy 新手教程' %>" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="<%= pageSeo.description || 'WorkBuddy 新手落地页：3步快速上手与实战场景提示词。' %>" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="<%= pageSeo.url || '' %>" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="<%= pageSeo.title || 'WorkBuddy 新手教程' %>" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="<%= pageSeo.description || 'WorkBuddy 新手落地页：3步快速上手与实战场景提示词。' %>" />
  <style>
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@400;600&display=swap");

    :root {
      --bg-0: #060811;
      --bg-1: #0a1430;
      --bg-2: #13274f;
      --cyan: #3df5ff;
      --cyan-soft: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.35);
      --line: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.8);
      --panel: rgba(8, 20, 50, 0.72);
      --panel-border: rgba(96, 137, 255, 0.35);
      --text-main: #dff9ff;
      --text-sub: #91aac7;
      --disabled: #4c5e76;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100%;
      color: var(--text-main);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 14%, rgba(79, 159, 255, 0.22), transparent 36%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 76%, rgba(0, 255, 230, 0.16), transparent 42%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, var(--bg-0), var(--bg-1) 48%, var(--bg-2));
      font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before,
    body::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    body::before {
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 42px 42px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 30%, transparent 82%);
      opacity: 0.45;
    }

    body::after {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.08), transparent);
      transform: translateY(-100%);
      animation: scanner 5.4s linear infinite;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    @keyframes scanner {
      to {
        transform: translateY(100%);
      }
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 68px 16px;
    }

    .steps {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 680px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 38px;
      padding: 34px 26px 36px;
      border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--panel), rgba(7, 17, 43, 0.52));
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 1px rgba(96, 137, 255, 0.12),
        0 24px 56px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45),
        inset 0 0 80px rgba(39, 80, 163, 0.15);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .step {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 96px;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: linear-gradient(130deg, rgba(17, 42, 88, 0.9), rgba(8, 24, 58, 0.75));
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: "Orbitron", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.4);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06),
        0 0 16px var(--cyan-soft);
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease, border-color 0.22s ease;
    }

    .step-main {
      display: block;
    }

    .step-note {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      text-align: center;
      text-shadow: none;
    }

    .step::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -120% -20%;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 40%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25) 50%, transparent 60%);
      transform: translateX(-24%);
      transition: transform 0.35s ease;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .step:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: #8ffaff;
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14),
        0 0 28px rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.52);
    }

    .step:hover::before {
      transform: translateX(28%);
    }

    .step:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .step.disabled {
      background: linear-gradient(130deg, rgba(17, 24, 45, 0.95), rgba(8, 13, 27, 0.85));
      border-color: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.36);
      color: var(--text-main);
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.24);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      pointer-events: none;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .title {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-size: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: "Orbitron", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
    }

    .headline {
      margin: 2px 0 6px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: #eefbff;
      font-family: "Orbitron", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.28);
    }

    .subline {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .panel {
      position: relative;
      padding: 22px 20px 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.24);
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(10, 23, 54, 0.92), rgba(7, 13, 28, 0.9));
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    }

    .panel::before {
      content: "SYSTEM CAPABILITIES";
      position: absolute;
      top: -10px;
      left: 16px;
      padding: 0 8px;
      background: #0b1430;
      color: rgba(143, 250, 255, 0.78);
      font-family: "Orbitron", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    }

    .panel-title {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: #eefbff;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-family: "Orbitron", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
    }

    .panel-copy {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .panel-tip {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.18);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.05);
      color: #cfeeff;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .chips {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .chip {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.22);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #dff9ff;
      background: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.08);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .feature-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .feature {
      padding: 14px 14px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(96, 137, 255, 0.22);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    }

    .feature strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: #f2fdff;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .feature span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── Tab system ── */
    .tab-bar {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .tab-btn {
      appearance: none;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      line-height: 1.3;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    .tab-btn:hover {
      color: #d0f6ff;
      border-color: rgba(143, 250, 255, 0.55);
      background: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.1);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .tab-btn.active {
      color: #031325;
      border-color: #8ffaff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8ffaff, #57d8ff);
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .tab-btn.is-hidden {
      display: none;
    }

    .industry-filter {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 2px 0 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .filter-label {
      color: rgba(143, 250, 255, 0.8);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .filter-btn {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.24);
      background: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.06);
      color: var(--text-sub);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .filter-btn.active {
      color: #041326;
      background: #76faff;
      border-color: #8ffaff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.35);
    }

    .tab-pane { display: none; }

    .tab-pane.active {
      display: block;
      animation: fadein 0.22s ease;
    }

    @keyframes fadein {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(5px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .pane-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .pane-title {
      margin: 0;
      flex: 1;
      color: #f3fdff;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-family: "Orbitron", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .copy-btn {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.3);
      background: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.08);
      color: #dff9ff;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      white-space: nowrap;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .copy-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      border-color: rgba(143, 250, 255, 0.65);
      background: rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.14);
    }

    .case-desc {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .meta-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .meta-block {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.14);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    }

    .meta-label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: rgba(143, 250, 255, 0.82);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .meta-text {
      display: block;
      color: #d8f6ff;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .prompt-label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: rgba(143, 250, 255, 0.7);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .prompt-box {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(61, 245, 255, 0.18);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(4, 10, 24, 0.8);
      color: #ebfdff;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
      font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, monospace;
    }

    .page-footer {
      margin-top: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(207, 238, 255, 0.82);
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .visitor-count {
      color: #8ffaff;
      font-family: "Orbitron", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 4px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .page {
        padding: 28px 14px;
      }

      .steps {
        max-width: 100%;
        gap: 24px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 24px 14px 20px;
      }

      .step {
        min-height: 82px;
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .headline {
        font-size: 28px;
      }

      .feature-list {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .panel-title {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .meta-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .tab-bar {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .pane-header {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .pane-title {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="steps" aria-label="Workbuddy 新手步骤">
      <p class="title">Workbuddy Onboarding</p>
      <h1 class="headline">快速接入流程</h1>
      <p class="subline">按顺序完成步骤，即可开始体验</p>

      <a class="step" href="https://t.vncps.com/7Ogc5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        1. 注册腾讯云账号
      </a>

      <a class="step" href="https://copilot.tencent.com/work/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        2. 下载 workbuddy
      </a>

      <div class="step disabled" aria-disabled="true">
        <span class="step-main">3. 打开 WorkBuddy 开始使用</span>
        <span class="step-note">安装完成后，手动打开客户端，选择“代码开发”或“日常办公”，然后新建你的第一个任务。</span>
      </div>

      <section class="panel" aria-label="Workbuddy 实战场景">
        <h2 class="panel-title">4. 实战场景指南</h2>
        <p class="panel-copy">选择下方任一场景，把提示词复制到 WorkBuddy 客户端，再把 <code style="background:rgba(61,245,255,0.1);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px">{{变量}}</code> 替换成你自己的内容，直接运行即可。</p>

        <div class="industry-filter" role="group" aria-label="按行业筛选案例">
          <span class="filter-label">行业筛选</span>
          <button class="filter-btn active" type="button" data-industry-filter="all">全部行业</button>
          <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-industry-filter="office">通用办公</button>
          <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-industry-filter="marketing">内容营销</button>
          <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-industry-filter="analysis">商业分析</button>
          <button class="filter-btn" type="button" data-industry-filter="finance">金融服务</button>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-bar" role="tablist" aria-label="选择场景">
          <button class="tab-btn active" role="tab" data-tab="pane-files" data-industry="office" aria-selected="true">🗂 桌面文件整理</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" data-tab="pane-video" data-industry="marketing" aria-selected="false">🎬 视频生成</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" data-tab="pane-research" data-industry="analysis" aria-selected="false">🔎 深度研究</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" data-tab="pane-ppt" data-industry="office" aria-selected="false">📑 幻灯片（PPT）</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" data-tab="pane-data" data-industry="analysis" aria-selected="false">📊 数据分析</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" data-tab="pane-viz" data-industry="analysis" aria-selected="false">📈 数据可视化</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" data-tab="pane-finance" data-industry="finance" aria-selected="false">💰 金融服务</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" data-tab="pane-product" data-industry="marketing" aria-selected="false">📣 产品宣发</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" data-tab="pane-pr" data-industry="marketing" aria-selected="false">📡 舆情监控</button>
        </div>

        <div id="pane-files" class="tab-pane active" data-industry="office" role="tabpanel">
          <div class="pane-header">
            <h3 class="pane-title">桌面文件整理</h3>
            <button class="copy-btn" type="button" data-copy-target="prompt-files">复制提示词</button>
          </div>
          <p class="case-desc">下载文件夹杂乱？WorkBuddy 会自动识别文件类型、按主题归类，全程不删除文件，最后输出整理报告供你确认。</p>
          <div class="meta-row">
            <div class="meta-block">
              <span class="meta-label">适用场景</span>
              <span class="meta-text">桌面杂乱、下载目录混杂、票据和合同散落、多格式文件需要统一归档。</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-block">
              <span class="meta-label">预期结果</span>
              <span class="meta-text">自动分类文件、建立清晰目录、标记疑似重复文件，并输出整理摘要。</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="prompt-label">提示词 — 复制后粘贴到 WorkBuddy 新任务</span>
          <pre class="prompt-box" id="prompt-files">请帮我整理本地文件夹中的文件。

目标文件夹：{{把这里替换为你的文件夹路径}}

请按下面要求执行：
1. 扫描该文件夹中的所有文件和子文件夹。
2. 按文件类型和内容主题进行分类，例如：图片、视频、文档、表格、合同、发票、安装包、压缩包、其他。
3. 如有必要，创建清晰的新目录结构，并将文件移动到对应目录。
4. 对名称混乱的文件，按"日期 + 类型 + 简短说明"的方式进行规范命名，但不要破坏原始扩展名。
5. 标记可能重复的文件，单独放入"疑似重复文件"目录，不要直接删除。
6. 最后输出一份整理报告，包括：共处理多少文件、创建了哪些目录、重命名了哪些文件、发现了哪些疑似重复文件。

执行原则：
- 优先安全，不要删除文件。
- 如果遇到无法判断分类的文件，放入"待确认"目录。
- 先给出执行计划，再开始处理。</pre>
        </div>

        <div id="pane-video" class="tab-pane" data-industry="marketing" role="tabpanel">
          <div class="pane-header">
            <h3 class="pane-title">视频生成</h3>
            <button class="copy-btn" type="button" data-copy-target="prompt-video">复制提示词</button>
          </div>
          <p class="case-desc">从主题到脚本、镜头设计、字幕文案一次生成，适合短视频账号持续产出内容。</p>
          <div class="meta-row">
            <div class="meta-block">
              <span class="meta-label">适用场景</span>
              <span class="meta-text">知识科普视频、产品演示视频、账号日更脚本、直播切片重制。</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-block">
              <span class="meta-label">预期结果</span>
              <span class="meta-text">输出完整分镜脚本、旁白文案、字幕稿、封面标题建议和发布描述。</span>
            </div>
          </div>
